<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c550a1c8e17ef07367063c6f1e0d5bf3>.
<#c550a1c8e17ef07367063c6f1e0d5bf3> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d7568ec4-d9e0-4f8f-bf01-e9f672a79198>;
