    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "High frequency temperature profiles are measured in lakes of SITES Water to be able to determine the thermal structure.\nErken Laboratory (2026). Physical variables - lake temperature profile from Erken, year-round anchored TW-profile, 2017-06-28–2025-12-01 [Data set]. Swedish Infrastructure for Ecosystem Science (SITES). https://hdl.handle.net/11676.1/gVQYm0aNPryFRtn2CpeuzzwF"@en, "High frequency temperature profiles are measured in lakes of SITES Water to be able to determine the thermal structure.\nErken Laboratory (2026). Physical variables - lake temperature profile from Erken, year-round anchored TW-profile, 2017-06-29–2025-11-30 [Data set]. Swedish Infrastructure for Ecosystem Science (SITES). https://hdl.handle.net/11676.1/wGiZX7JjzAt6ZmD_V1msIID_"@en;
