    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Artifact package for the study \"When GUI-based Testing Meets Code Reviews\".\n\n01_Interview_transcriptions.zip: All transcribed and anonymized interviews\n\n02_QDA.zip: All data related to the qualitative data analysis (QDA) of interviews. This includes the codebook (all versions of it), the tool with an export of the data, and the final coding by two coders and their diff."@en;
