    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__5347.
_:b0__5347 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/7c5eb3248d6ad10e54a856d6bdd6c306>;
